========================= Follow below steps ============================

1. First, set up the BigCommerce theme on Stencil.

2. Go to the templates > pages folder (directory).

3. Inside the pages folder, create a new folder named custom.

4. Now create a file to display the custom product template, for example: new-template.html.

5. Then copy the default product template code and paste it into new-template.html. Update the code according to your requirements.
